The dresses we have to cut them from the magazines or search them on the internet and print them, to then elaborate them graphically.
The moodboard, which is what the full result is called, also expresses our personal style and our relationship with graphic design.
It is also important to think about the graphic part of styling.
The stylist, therefore, does not only dress physically, but also deals, for example, with product pages in magazines (concrete topics, such as trends, bags, coats, etc.).
The designer and designer Mario Kameník told us about all of this.
